is there an easy way to get the block achievement on march madness for i can't even come close i've adjusted some sliders nothing is helping to start this is a very hard achievement for the xbox but once you know what to do it can be very easy make sure you have stats with the team your profile is controlling and the other team controlled by a second controller has their stats set to now make sure the second player point guard gets the ball and move him somewhere around the point line next put your point guard relativity close to the second player point guard with the ball this is where it gets a little tricky because you have to do this at the right time the second player with the ball has to hold b and right after they do that the you must press y fast if the ball gets knocked away you have done this successfully if the ball gets shot you either pressed y too early or too late this is best done with a friend good luck if you need more help check out the achievement guides by following the link in the source Rinoa Heartilly Squall Leonhart Final Fantasy VIII Final Fantasy Tactics Advance Laguna Loire Final Fantasy X Final Fantasy X-2 Limit Break Cid (Final Fantasy) Final Fantasy airships Avenue Q Cid Pollendina Wheel of Fortune Final Fantasy III Joke Final Fantasy VII Final Fantasy: The Spirits Within Cid Highwind Match Game The Wizard of Oz (1939 film) Final Fantasy II Seifer Almasy Final Fantasy The Beach Boys Final Fantasy Tactics Video game music Final Fantasy IV Kingdom Hearts II Rowan & Martin's Laugh-In Final Fantasy IX Garden (Final Fantasy VIII) Aladdin (1992 film) Milton H. Erickson Final Fantasy VI Quistis Trepe Before Crisis: Final Fantasy VII Chocobo Racing Final Fantasy: Crystal Chronicles Computer role-playing game The Ashlee Simpson Show Ragnarok (Final Fantasy) Late Night with Conan O'Brien Final Fantasy magic Mirmo! Celes Ch__re Tifa Lockheart Britney Spears Age of Wonders The Krypton Factor Final Fantasy character classes Dirge of Cerberus: Final